{"tid":594382,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人生過成人痘/壓力瘡？","createTime":"2018-03-15T19:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T18:19:06.000Z","uid":88967,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b68358f6d1e0518d15d22c07a36b9096b1c2557c","tid":594382,"uid":88967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T19:25:31.000Z","msg":"宜家大約二十頭，之前做嘢太辛苦壓力太大，臉頰兩邊同下巴都生唔少細細粒既膿頭，好多好似係閉合性暗瘡，㩒唔出膿。兩個月左右發現唔對路去睇醫生，先知係咁簡單。<br />\n<br />\n結果醫生話應該係由內分泌失調同壓力引起既口周皮炎(Perioral dermatitis)，開咗d藥膏俾我搽。大概過咗兩三個月後d膿頭已經好得七七八八，冇再冒起，但依然仲有好多印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人試過類似咁既情況？有冇去印好方法推薦？<br />\n<br />\n利申：借朋友AC"},{"pid":"74d197a95309615f8b64915fc32f691db0b6db43","tid":594382,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T19:31:59.000Z","msg":"睇埋中醫lor    中醫調理方面比西醫好"},{"pid":"68671fd8ded5b49ea108d90394aa3877d6aa48e1","tid":594382,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T19:32:41.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n<br />\n呢4,5年都 壓力大"},{"pid":"d612c8e628d71f40f0528bb6039e1cfd72630a5b","tid":594382,"uid":88967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T19:36:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有<br />\n<br />\n呢4,5年都 壓力大</blockquote><br />\n咁你宜家情況如何呀？"},{"pid":"7cb3705b74077dec0c5286a8d37e6b808a2dd8d7","tid":594382,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T19:59:53.000Z","msg":"有 仲大過時昌迷你瘡"},{"pid":"9f750bc7453c7ced0999ccca25235b8db4ea805f","tid":594382,"uid":88967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T14:51:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec7d4aeb0660e7d358244a2dd22085760929983a","tid":594382,"uid":3287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T15:00:14.000Z","msg":"同你一模一樣 近排返工辛苦愈生愈多<br />\n宜家我知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal